phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common coroutine ViewModel mistakes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| GlobalScope | Use `viewModelScope` |
| No error handling | Add `try-catch` |
| No loading state | Add `isLoading` |
| Heavy on main | Use `Dispatchers.Default` |
| No collect | Use `collectAsState()` |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use viewModelScope
viewModelScope.launch { /* work */ }

// 2. Handle errors
try {
    val data = getData()
    _state.value = data
} catch (e: Exception) {
    _error.value = e.message
}

// 3. Show loading
_isLoading.value = true
try { /* work */ } finally { _isLoading.value = false }

// 4. Use proper dispatcher
withContext(Dispatchers.Default) {
    // Heavy computation
}

// 5. Collect state
val state by viewModel.state.collectAsState()
```

